data.description: 959 Glide Loop Dr is a charming residential property situated in the scenic peaceful and tranquil living environment. The property features a spacious and well-maintained house that is perfect for a family or those seeking a comfortable retreat.  This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home on 1.47 acres offers ample space for both indoor and outdoor activities. This home has a great open floor plan with large windows that give you an amazing view of the river. The outdoor space is equally as impressive as the home, with this well-maintained yard that is fully fenced making it great for outdoor entertaining. Lets not forget your own fishing spot on the river. It also has plenty of parking and storage in the large 3 bay shop and large driveway. A rare find don't miss out.
